<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbbb5d569-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s2000c–7"><num value="2000c–7">§ 2000c–7.</num><heading> Liability of United States for costs</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In any action or proceeding under this subchapter the United States shall be liable for costs the same as a private person.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbbb5d56a-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/88/352/tIV/s408">Pub. L. 88–352, title IV, § 408</ref>, <date date="1964-07-02">July 2, 1964</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/78/249">78 Stat. 249</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
